text: Zibo () is a prefecture-level city in central Shandong province, China. In 2020, 4,704,138 people lived there. == Administration == Zibo administers five districts and three counties: * Boshan District () * Gaoqing County () * Huantai County () * Linzi District () * Yiyuan County () * Zhangdian District () * Zhoucun District () * Zichuan District () Category:Cities in China Category:Shandong
title: Zibo
